Package: r2webstat
Title: Client for the Banque de France Webstat API
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Author: rwebstat, updated by Jeremi Montornes
Maintainer: Jeremi Montornes <jeremi.montornes@gmail.com>
Description: Access the redesigned Banque de France Webstat portal through
    its Huwise/Opendatasoft Explore API. The package provides helpers for
    catalog metadata, Webstat datasets, series metadata, observations, facets,
    and export URLs.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
URL: https://github.com/JeremiMontornes/r2webstat
BugReports: https://github.com/JeremiMontornes/r2webstat/issues
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1)
Imports:
    httr2
Suggests:
    ggplot2,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
